title: Transformers (2019 IDW Reboot)
description: Includes the main series and all the spin-offs and side material of the IDW 2019 Transformers reboot. Each chapter corresponds to its respective volume colllecting the individual issues. Vols. 1 to 5 are rips from the official source and vol. 6 is a fan made collection of the remaining issues.
author: Brian Ruckley et al.
